敵が近くにいる場合も
『潜伏』を即時起動します。
煙玉の状態異常発生率は
命中に依存します。]], "tformat")
t("Aim", "百発百中の構え", "talent name")
t([[Enter a calm, focused stance, increasing physical power and accuracy by %d, projectile speed by %d%% and the chance to mark targets by an additional %d%%.
